*The FCC photos indicate this device has a :single USB 2.0 and a single USB 3.0 port.
*[[ASUS RT-AC55U]] - 2x 3dBi external antenna *[[ASUS RT-AC55UHP]] - 2x 9dBi external antenna
Default settings are per the FCC label.
===Specifications=== *Product class: ''AC1200'' (300Mbps [2.4GHz] + 867Mbps [5GHz]) *Antennas: 2x external 9dBi dipole antenna w/ RP-SMA connector *Ports: USB: 1x ''USB 2.0'', 1x ''USB 3.0'' :Ethernet: 1x WAN, 4x LAN (10/100/1000 Base-T) *Power Supply: :AC Input: 110~240V (50~60Hz) :DC Output: 12V with max. 2A current *Vendor firmware operation modes: :wireless router, access point, media bridge *Vendor firmware features: :''AiCloud'', USB file/printer/scanner sharing ([http://www.asus.com/Networking/RTAC55UHP/ PPage]) :''ASUSWRT'' interface, ''Smart QoS'' ([https://www.qca.qualcomm.com/products/qualcomm-streamboost/ StreamBoost])
